PrecisAuthority (a) for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION, as lessor, to enter into a new sixty-six (66) year leasing arrangement with HAB-COM LIMITED with respect to the redevelopment of the JEANNE D'ARC INSTITUTE at 489 Sussex Drive in Ottawa, (b) to enter into Encroachment Agreements with both the Regional Municipality of Ottawa-Carleton and the City of Ottawa, (c) to assign the rights thereby acquired to the lessee, and (d) to revoke Order in Council P.C. 1993-2/2139.
